import React,{useEffect,useState} from 'react' import {useHistory} from 'react-router-dom' import axios from 'axios' function Post() { const [result1,setresult1] = useState([]) let history=useHistory(); useEffect(() => { if(!localStorage.getItem('Token')) { history.push('./login') } axios.get('http://localhost:5000').then(result=>{ setresult1(result.data) }) }, []) return ( <> { (result1.length!==0)?result1.map(val=>{
Dogs
{val.name}
{val.time}
